<br>
Guilds and players tend to choose policies that suit them the best.  If IV was to disappear, with every member vanishing, another guild with similar policies would appear.<br>
<br>
There are exceptions of course, of note, Zozz leaving IV because he didn't agree with our policies.  I admire him for his conviction, even if I don't agree with his motivation.<br>
<br>
There's an amusing situation on Lanys.  The big guild there, Conquest, was disbanded by Verant, and most of the members quit EQ as they felt the decision was unjust.  There was another guild, perhaps once the second largest on the server named Inner Fire.  They battled with CQ on the message boards, fighting for opportunities to kill big mobs that CQ killed quickly and efficiently before other guilds.  <br>
<br>
With CQ and almost all of its members gone however, the bulk of IF disbanded and formed a new guild in CQ's image, with many members forsaking the values that they preached for a year, while fighting CQ while in IF.<br>
<br>
There are stories like this on many servers, if not all of them.  If it's not the top guild falling, it's people who opposed that guild joining.<br>
<br>
The fact is, high level EQ is played in a certain way, and this is it.  It's a reality.  Please don't bitch and whine to IV because you don't like how the upper level game is played. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/usilvirthewizard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Silvir the Wizard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Junior Member</span><br>  Posts: 62<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(7/25/01 2:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=57>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> Umm ok.  The whole thing of &quot;this is how its done on other servers, so don't get angry at us&quot;.. whatever. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FFFFFF>- </font><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter>Vazaelle.com Community Center</a><font color=#FFFFFF> - </font><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm24>VCC Archives</a> <font color=#FFFFFF> - </font><a href="http://www.vazaelle.com">Vazaelle.com</a><font color=#FFFFFF> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.246j<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

